OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1779706980
OL,3,CMurder investigation launched in
OL,4,CMiddlesbrough as woman arrested
OL,6,FA woman has been arrested and a
OL,7,Fsearches are taking place for a second
OL,8,Fsuspect after a man was murdered in
OL,9,FMiddlesbrough.
OL,11,FOfficers were called to Ayton Crescent
OL,12,Fin Eston at around 11pm on Saturday
OL,13,Fnight (23rd May). They found a man who
OL,14,Fwas then pronounced dead at the scene.
OL,16,FA 39-year-old woman was arrested, and
OL,17,FCleveland Police say they are trying
OL,18,Fto find a second suspect.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/3
