OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1779706980
OL,3,CMurder investigation launched in
OL,4,CMiddlesbrough as woman arrested
OL,6,FSuperintendent Daryll Tomlinson, who
OL,7,Fhas led the investigation overnight,
OL,8,Fsaid:
OL,10,F"This is a fast-moving investigation,
OL,11,Fand we have quickly made an arrest. I
OL,12,Fwould like to thank members of the
OL,13,Fpublic who have come forward with
OL,14,Finformation, as well as the National
OL,15,FPolice Air Service for their support
OL,16,Fthrough the night."
OL,26,@rD@AOU
