PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1779706980
OL,3,CMurder investigation launched in
OL,4,CMiddlesbrough as woman arrested
OL,6,F"I would like to reassure the
OL,7,Fcommunity that this is an isolated
OL,8,Fincident, with no wider risk to the
OL,9,Fpublic. Officers will remain at the
OL,10,Fscene in Ayton Crescent, and there
OL,11,Fwill be an increased presence in the
OL,12,Farea.
